{"tid":240444,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"大銀幕比石仔彈到","createTime":"2017-05-12T12:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T08:47:36.000Z","uid":11284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"454fffc055de55c3b2590dadb247785521641fa9","tid":240444,"uid":11284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"前幾日揸緊車無啦啦有粒石仔'啪'一聲 之後大銀幕就姴左了<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ba4798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ba4798.jpg&h=33a5c1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/200403_5281b6dd53dc610c2a92482a65255b29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F200403_5281b6dd53dc610c2a92482a65255b29.jpg&h=cb67fe04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係乘客位望落去非常明顯黑左一條咁<br />\n換過塊玻璃又要幾千蚊...唉我d窮撚就上淘寶睇下<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/200538_4f8789f209bf43345caa409b82928665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F200538_4f8789f209bf43345caa409b82928665.jpg&h=eefc2ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有成千好評咁就試下啦,琴日就到左手,希望可以救得番<br />\n有沒巴絲有用過類似產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a628fc97c52a45c55d36afa7a42f3ef210500a","tid":240444,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"雜嘜牌子唔洗幾千啦"},{"pid":"af76bc0bbdfb9e4a204816000b83a85f24f33de3","tid":240444,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"崩左就補到<br />\n裂成咁一定要換"},{"pid":"d1ef1968d4c35cec3f5b0b087931e846ecf7d3b8","tid":240444,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日揸緊車無啦啦有粒石仔'啪'一聲 之後大銀幕就姴左了<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ba4798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ba4798.jpg&h=33a5c1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><im